summary: Angelicus is a all round Fighter, seen it, done it, fought it. He will level with you, protect you and marry you. He lives in secret inside Breezehome, a lovely surprise to find after you purchase the house.
descriptionHtml:
Angelicus is a all round Fighter, seen it, done it, fought it. He will level with you, protect you and marry you. He lives in secret inside Breezehome, a lovely surprise to find after you purchase the house.
Mods I used to make this beast:


Better males - Beautiful nudes and faces - New hairstyles

ApachiiSkyHair   (This is a must or he wont work) Make sure it is before Angelicus in load order please.

Witcher Ultimate Experience. For the outfit. 

PS. He is not wearing this outfit when you get him, I just think it looks sexy on him. You will have to dress him as you like.
author: Lycanheart
